OL,3,C'Heartbroken isn't the word': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son pays tribute
OL,6,FThe son of boxing legend Ricky Hatton,
OL,7,FCampbell Hatton, has spoken publicly
OL,8,Ffor the first time since the death of
OL,9,Fhis father, paying tribute in an
OL,10,Femotional Instagram post.
OL,12,FTributes have poured in across the
OL,13,Fworld of sport and beyond following
OL,14,Fthe death of Hatton, a former world
OL,15,Fwelterweight champion, who died on
OL,16,FSunday aged 46.
OL,18,F"Heartbroken isn't the word," his son
OL,19,Fcaptioned the series of family photos.
