OL,6,F"Everybody has always said I was your
OL,7,Fdouble ` never a truer word said.
OL,8,FLooked up to you in every aspect of
OL,9,Flife."
OL,11,FHe added: "Can't explain how much I'm
OL,12,Fgoing to miss the laughs we had and
OL,13,Fall the good times, which I will
OL,14,Fremember forever. Just can't believe
OL,15,Fwe won't have any more. Love you, Dad."
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police said the
OL,18,Fboxing legend had been found dead at
OL,19,Fhis home in Hyde, Greater Manchester.
OL,20,FThe police said there were no
OL,21,Fsuspicious circumstances.
