OL,3,C'Heartbroken isn't the word': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son pays tribute
OL,6,FLike his father, Campbell pursued a
OL,7,Fcareer in boxing, making his
OL,8,Fprofessional debut in 2021. He retired
OL,9,Ffrom the sport earlier this year.
OL,11,FOn Monday, the former world
OL,12,Fwelterweight champion's family issued
OL,13,Fa statement via police, saying they
OL,14,Fwere "deeply moved" by the outpouring
OL,15,Fof love and support towards him.
OL,17,F"Richard was so much more than a world
OL,18,Fchampion. To us he was simply
OL,19,F'Richard', our son. A loving father,
OL,20,Fgrandfather and brother, and a true
OL,21,Ffriend to many," the statement read.
